# Definition of Done

**Full checklist:** [`docs/DEFINITION-OF-DONE.md`](../../docs/DEFINITION-OF-DONE.md)

## Task is NOT complete until

1. **Scope** — Matches `docs/TODO.md` item for active program in `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md`
2. **Build** — `npm run build` passes (functions build if backend touched)
3. **Smoke** — Area-specific smoke green (matrix in `PROJECT_STATE.md`)
4. **Self-review** — `ai-governance-self-review.mdc` checklist passed
5. **Docs** — `TODO`, `DASHBOARD`, `PROGRESS` updated; `ROADMAP` if program phase changed; `PROJECT_STATE` if system phase/blockers changed
6. **PMIR** — No forbidden changes without Pontus OK

